node.text:
who gave their time to be on No Filter with Naomi .  Celebrating our 1 st Anniversary !!Started this by putting my IPAD on a pile of books on my dinning table , dressed sometimes from waist up !! .. I hope this has  bought some polite distraction hearing our conversations  in these challenging times , to  @kindredmediahq  @aryehbourkoff and @sidrasmithofficial @essence for stepping in to sponsor and keeping the wheels turning .. and to my incredible team who have been there since day 1 @derekblasberg, @stevengrossman , Alex Kovacs, @chamberschris, Blythe , Peter and Sam at shortcuts @Terripitts @akeemjr... #Sasha @shortcutsediting 
Thank you , love  to you all ❤️❤️❤️❤️ @cindycrawford @diddy @carlabruniofficial @cturlington @nicolerichie @themarcjacobs @ashleygraham @pppiccioli @leedaniels @adutakech @sharonstone @parishilton @venuswilliams @serenawilliams @karliekloss @jackieaina @opalayo @real_sharpton @alphonsodavid @bethannhardison @tylersphotos @cynthiaerivo @chrisrock @katehudson @gabunion @therealmaryjblige @jamescharles @whoopigoldberg @chelseahandler @camerondiaz @femiakuti @iamishasesay @lizakoshy @thepatriciabright @lilly @mariahcarey @drseemayasmin @wizkidayo @majimb.o @goldarosheuvel @andradaymusic @rayformayor @traceeellisross @bravoandy @pharrell @jpgaultierofficial @sholamos1 @parisjackson @davechappelle 🙏🏾❤️

node.title: To My Panthers , So grateful  to all these  amazing Guests

node.text:
lpeopleswagner you are a force!! 
It’s an honor to be on your 1st Issue of The Cut .. This shoot was shot smack bang in middle of August when mostly our industry is shut down .. It took , Trains .Planes snd automobiles to bring us all together , in this very difficult time of travel .. I’m Proud of the whole Team , I still count on one hand of how many shoots I have done where pretty much the  entire team is same color as me .  After 35 years it’s finally happening . I don’t know  weather to jump or  cry tears of joy , but all  who knows me .. knows ok what’s the Next level to conquer .  As we take our  rightfully owned  positions .. Thank you @campbelladdy , Knew you were going to be a star ⭐️ , with keeping to your integrity and style , the day  we met 4 years ago you answered my dm and we met for tea !!’ And Jess  @jessswill so excited for what’s lays ahead of you.  @anglomamakeup and  @lorenzo_barcel  my Fam mad love for you  both always .. proud to be in this issue with my sisters and all it stands for 💜🙏🏾
Thank  you @richardhabberley and @chamberschris 💕
And Desiree  Ejoh for watching over me 💖
 #September #Issue

node.text: Happy Birthday my darling Theaster @theastergates , may this day continue to bestow many more blessings to you !! I hold so much love admiration and respect for you , how you uplift everyday our culture young artists , creatives  constantly putting us forward , !! Will never forget seeing your show in miami , then @pppiccioli bringing it to life and calling you  to tell  and ask you if you could come to Paris .and you had just landed from China ! Guess  where ……. Paris ,so ment  to be , so happy you got to be there and witness that  and oh Let’s NOT FORGET TO LET PEOPLE KNOW HOW YOU SING ( PLS SCROLL) !! Blessed I got to witness that .. I love you chosen family ❤️🎂❤️🎂❤️🎂
